50|$|The Booksellers Association of the UK and Ireland (BA) is a {{trade body}} founded to promote retail {{bookselling}} in the United Kingdom and Ireland. It operates the National Book Token scheme in the UK and sponsors the Whitbread Award The BA represents 95% of British <b>retail</b> <b>booksellers.</b> The BA operates the Batch payments system, an electronic purchasing interface for independent bookshops.|$|R
